The paper deals with scene text detection using convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method also involves segmentation and post-processing, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the challenges of text detection in natural scenes, which is a topic in computational linguistics (cs.CL) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
